episodes.title: She Got Kicked Out of a Cult and Didn’t Even Know It
episodes.description:
Gabby dives into the most chaotic religion story she’s ever heard: a girl who got kicked out of a cult simply for not volunteering. Suddenly, there’s Catholic guilt, Staten Island accents, childhood confusion, and zero actual witnessing of Jehovah. It’s messy, unhinged, and way too relatable for anyone who’s ever switched religions like outfits.

ABOUT GABBY:

Gabby Bryan is a New York-based stand-up comedian, actress, Emmy-award winning producer, and overall girlie girl. She performed alongside Olivia Wilde and Oscar Isaac in the film “Life Itself” (Amazon Prime), appeared in the bilingual film “Ruta Viva” (HBO), and featured in Ilana Glazer’s special “Comedy on Earth” (Comedy Central). Gabby co-hosts "Let Me Ask My Dad” Podcast with musician and composer and her dad David Bryan. She has toured all around the globe and continues with her sold out show "GABBY BRYAN IS MY BESTFRIEND". She is wildly popular on social media with over 450K+ followers, sharing viral stand up clips & comedy sketches.
